| Name | Example | Usage | | :--- | :--- | :--- | | **[autorole\|autoroles]** | !autoroles | Shows which roles will be added upon joining and if the bot will readd roles when someone leaves and rejoins the server | | **autorole [readd\|reassign]** | !autorole readd | Turns reassigning roles on/off | | **autorole add &lt;role&gt;** | !autorole add peon | Autoroles are roles that are given to the user upon joining the server. | | **autorole remove &lt;role&gt;** | !autorole remove admin | Removes a role from being auto assigned | | **autorole [bl\|blacklist] &lt;roles...&gt;** | !autorole bl admin newbie | Prevents the mentioned roles from being reassigned | | **autorole unblacklist &lt;roles...&gt;** | !autorole unblacklist "fortnite expert" admin | Undoes what !autorole bl does |
